                                <rect key="frame" x="16" y="338" width="361" height="107"/>
                                <autoresizingMask key="autoresizingMask" flexibleMaxX="YES" flexibleMaxY="YES"/>
                                <string key="text">This is the movie that changed everything.For the first time, Iron Man, Captain America, Thor, the Hulk, Black Widow, and Hawkeye are brought together by Nick Fury.They must learn to work as a team to stop Thor’s mischievous brother, Loki, and his alien army from invading New York City.</string>
