                                <rect key="frame" x="16" y="633" width="361" height="106"/>
                                <autoresizingMask key="autoresizingMask" flexibleMaxX="YES" flexibleMaxY="YES"/>
                                <string key="text">Often called "Avengers 2.5," this film splits the team into two factions. One side is led by Captain America, who wants independence, and the other by Iron Man, who supports government oversight. It’s an emotional rollercoaster that features almost every hero, including the debut of Spider-Man and Black Panther.</string>
